&lt;li&gt;Exceptional technical and problem-solving skills and reasoning ability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to prioritize and stay cool in a dynamic start-up environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to lift 50 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position may require travel up to up 30%.&lt;/li&gt;
